					"type": 23,
					"value": "Repeated sequential AD for the refugee family living inside the toymaker's house. This AD will be played in a loop after the refugees will be saved from the thugs and will be allowed to live inside (or, because thugs were dead or threatened - there's just no one to oblige)."
